mdes.slick.sui.event
Class KeyEvent

java.lang.Object
  mdes.slick.sui.event.EventObject
      mdes.slick.sui.event.KeyEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class KeyEvent
extends EventObject

A keyboard event, such as key press or key release. Each key event has a key code conforming to the Input key constants and a char value for the key.

Since:
b.0.2
